{"tid":2155503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬體會主席：若歐冠無法繼續 會方應頒冠軍給馬體會","createTime":"2020-08-13T22:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T02:04:04.000Z","uid":19552,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"313ddd7a96038fd3143a369ef06f3c81f2a9ce99","tid":2155503,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T22:34:04.000Z","msg":"近日接受媒體採訪時，馬競主席恩里克-塞雷佐稱，如果歐冠不能繼續進行，那麼應該把冠軍給馬競，因為馬競淘汰了利物浦。<br />\n<br />\n塞雷佐說道：&ldquo;如果歐冠因為疫情等原因不能正常進行了，那麼我覺得應該把冠軍頒發給擊敗上屆冠軍的球隊，這就像擂台賽。正常的賽制中，還有幾場1/ 8決賽沒踢完，後面還有1/4決賽、半決賽和決賽。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我覺得歐足聯應該試著將所有比賽都集中到同一城市中進行，有人說會在西班牙進行，有人說會在葡萄牙進行，但是現在什麼都還沒確定。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;聯賽還有11輪，歐冠可能還有4輪，我覺得政府是想等看後面疫情發展再決定吧。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9e755a02aeade13ca2ba11ca17abbf4c3fbbb66a","tid":2155503,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T22:43:33.000Z","msg":"牙益點睇球王felix 入波"},{"pid":"21216f07595dfb8d809a5f9865dd0ac001954abd","tid":2155503,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T23:07:05.000Z","msg":"馬體會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920269bea9bd39902a2d4f3ab4d0532eceb74c4a","tid":2155503,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T23:08:46.000Z","msg":"而家就收咗皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b56b355de144b6789ab238906681c49be2c767","tid":2155503,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T23:11:12.000Z","msg":"應該盼比Reipzig<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0513959bb4562787b43021e714d68cf996d389df","tid":2155503,"uid":247892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T23:14:10.000Z","msg":"今年既實力連德甲都不如"},{"pid":"2f19a29a87e74617905f2a2b9bd5660c65575992","tid":2155503,"uid":33642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T23:33:06.000Z","msg":"今日係咪返咗去攞獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder